      "blurb": "<span class=\"template_sbc\"><b>Recast:</b></span> <b>Galio</b> <span class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Taunt\"><a href=\"/wiki/Taunt\" title=\"Taunt\"><img alt=\"Taunt icon\" decoding=\"async\" data-image-key=\"Taunt_icon.png\" class=\"lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-relevant=\"0\" height=\"20\" width=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Taunt icon.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/6e/Taunt_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223944\"></a> <a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"/wiki/Taunt\" title=\"Taunt\">taunts</a></span> nearby enemy champions, dealing <span style=\"color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal\">magic damage</span>. The effects are increased based on charge time.",
