      "icon": "Hero's Entrance.png",
      "blurb": "<span class=\"template_sbc\"><b>Active:</b></span> <span style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-champion=\"Galio\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"inline-image label-after champion-icon\" data-skin=\"Original\" data-param=\"\"><span data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\" style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL\" title=\"Galio\"><img loading=\"lazy\" height=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-name=\"Galio OriginalSquare.png\" data-image-key=\"Galio_OriginalSquare.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8d/Galio_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170308183135\" data-relevant=\"0\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" alt=\"Galio\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a title=\"Galio/LoL\" href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL\">Galio</a></span></span> guards the target allied champion, <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Channels\"><a href=\"/wiki/Channel\" title=\"Channel\"><img height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/bb/Channeling_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180628192319\" class=\"lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-image-key=\"Channeling_icon.png\" width=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Channeling icon.png\" alt=\"Channeling icon\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\"></a> <a title=\"Channel\" href=\"/wiki/Channel\">channelling</a></span> for a short time and granting  <span data-ability=\"Shield of Durand\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\" data-param=\"\" data-champion=\"Galio\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"inline-image label-after ability-icon\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\"><a href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL#Shield_of_Durand\" title=\"his\"><img class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9b/Galio_Shield_of_Durand.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170317025025\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" alt=\"his\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-image-name=\"Galio Shield of Durand.png\" data-image-key=\"Galio_Shield_of_Durand.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL#Shield_of_Durand\" title=\"Galio/LoL\">his</a></span></span> <span style=\"color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal\">magic damage</span> <span class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Shield\" data-game=\"lol\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\"><a title=\"Shield\" href=\"/wiki/Shield\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Hybrid resistances icon.png\" alt=\"Hybrid resistances icon\" decoding=\"async\" data-relevant=\"0\" width=\"20\" data-image-key=\"Hybrid_resistances_icon.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Hybrid_resistances_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170516021237\" class=\"lazyload\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Shield\" title=\"Shield\">shield</a></span> to himself and all allied <span class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Champions\"><a title=\"Champion\" href=\"/wiki/Champion\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Champion icon.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/25/Champion_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20181122022630\" data-image-key=\"Champion_icon.png\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" alt=\"Champion icon\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Champion\" title=\"Champion\">champions</a></span> in the area.",
      "description": "<span class=\"template_sbc\"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Galio</b> prepares to make an entrance, <span class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Channel\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\"><a title=\"Channel\" href=\"/wiki/Channel\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/bb/Channeling_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180628192319\" alt=\"Channeling icon\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Channeling icon.png\" data-image-key=\"Channeling_icon.png\" height=\"20\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"lazyload\" data-relevant=\"0\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" width=\"20\"></a> <a title=\"Channel\" href=\"/wiki/Channel\">channeling</a></span> for 2.<small>75</small> seconds and designating the target allied <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" class=\"glossary\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Champion\"><a title=\"Champion\" href=\"/wiki/Champion\"><img data-image-name=\"Champion icon.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-key=\"Champion_icon.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/25/Champion_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20181122022630\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"20\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Champion icon\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Champion\" title=\"Champion\">champion's</a></span> location at the time of cast as his landing spot. Additionally, he resets <i><span data-champion=\"Galio\" data-ability=\"Shield of Durand 2\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"inline-image label-after ability-icon\" data-param=\"\" style=\"display:inline;white-space:pre;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;position:relative;\" data-width=\"20\" class=\"border\"><a href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL#Shield_of_Durand_2\" title=\"Shield of Durand's\"><img data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/07/Galio_Shield_of_Durand_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171221040440\" class=\"thumbborder lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-key=\"Galio_Shield_of_Durand_2.png\" data-image-name=\"Galio Shield of Durand 2.png\" alt=\"Shield of Durand's\"></a></span> <span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Galio/LoL#Shield_of_Durand_2\" title=\"Galio/LoL\">Shield of Durand's</a></span></span></i> passive shield for himself and grants it to all allied champions within the area for 5 seconds.",
