      "blurb": "After a short delay, <b>Galio</b> rises <span data-game=\"lol\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Cc-immune\"><a href=\"/wiki/Crowd_control#Immunity\" title=\"Crowd control\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-name=\"Cc-immune icon.png\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b1/Cc-immune_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200327223512\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" data-image-key=\"Cc-immune_icon.png\" alt=\"Cc-immune icon\" data-relevant=\"0\" class=\"lazyload\"></a> <a title=\"Crowd control\" href=\"/wiki/Crowd_control#Immunity\">unstoppably</a></span> and <span data-tip=\"Untargetable\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"glossary\"><a href=\"/wiki/Untargetable\" title=\"Untargetable\"><img data-image-name=\"Untargetable icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" data-relevant=\"0\" height=\"20\" data-image-key=\"Untargetable_icon.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Untargetable_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220206063243\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Untargetable icon\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Untargetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Untargetable\">intangibly</a></span> before <span data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Dash\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" class=\"glossary\"><a title=\"Dash\" href=\"/wiki/Dash\"><img data-image-name=\"Dash.png\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-relevant=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" alt=\"Dash\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826\" data-image-key=\"Dash.png\"></a> <a title=\"Dash\" href=\"/wiki/Dash\">crashing</a></span> down onto the target's initial location, dealing <span style=\"color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal\">magic damage</span> to nearby enemies and <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" class=\"glossary\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Airborne\"><a title=\"Airborne\" href=\"/wiki/Airborne\"><img alt=\"Airborne icon\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-relevant=\"0\" width=\"20\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d6/Airborne_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223933\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Airborne icon.png\" data-image-key=\"Airborne_icon.png\" class=\"lazyload\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Airborne\" title=\"Airborne\" class=\"mw-redirect\">knocking them back</a></span>.",
      "description": "After channeling for 1.<small>25</small> seconds, he gains <span data-tip=\"Cc-immune\" data-game=\"lol\" class=\"glossary\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\"><a title=\"Crowd control\" href=\"/wiki/Crowd_control#Immunity\"><img loading=\"lazy\" data-relevant=\"0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-name=\"Cc-immune icon.png\" class=\"lazyload\" width=\"20\" data-image-key=\"Cc-immune_icon.png\" alt=\"Cc-immune icon\" height=\"20\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b1/Cc-immune_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20200327223512\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Crowd_control#Immunity\" title=\"Crowd control\">crowd control immunity</a></span> for the remaining duration, becomes <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-game=\"lol\" data-tip=\"Untargetable\" class=\"glossary\"><a title=\"Untargetable\" href=\"/wiki/Untargetable\"><img decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" data-image-name=\"Untargetable icon.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-key=\"Untargetable_icon.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/41/Untargetable_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20220206063243\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" class=\"lazyload\" alt=\"Untargetable icon\"></a> <a title=\"Untargetable\" href=\"/wiki/Untargetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\">untargetable</a></span>, and leaps into the air for <span class=\"basic-tooltip\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;\" title=\"Estimated\">0.<small>85</small> seconds</span> before <span class=\"glossary\" data-game=\"lol\" style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" data-tip=\"Dash\"><a href=\"/wiki/Dash\" title=\"Dash\"><img height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-image-name=\"Dash.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"lazyload\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" data-image-key=\"Dash.png\" width=\"20\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826\" alt=\"Dash\"></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Dash\" title=\"Dash\">dashing</a></span> to his destination over <span style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;\" class=\"basic-tooltip\" title=\"Estimated\">0.<small>25</small> seconds</span>. Afterwards, he lands and becomes targetable again, dealing <span style=\"color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal\">magic damage</span> to all nearby enemies upon impact, <span style=\"white-space:pre; position:relative;\" class=\"glossary\" data-tip=\"Airborne\" data-game=\"lol\"><a href=\"/wiki/Airborne\" title=\"Airborne\"><img data-image-name=\"Airborne icon.png\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d6/Airborne_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223933\" width=\"20\" data-relevant=\"0\" alt=\"Airborne icon\" data-image-key=\"Airborne_icon.png\" class=\"lazyload\"></a> <a title=\"Airborne\" href=\"/wiki/Airborne\" class=\"mw-redirect\">knocking them back</a></span> 100 units over 0.<small>75</small> seconds, and remaining in place for <span class=\"basic-tooltip\" title=\"Estimated\" style=\"border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;\">0.<small>4</small> seconds</span>.",
